ygData.messageBody:
My guess is that your were still grouped and thus unable to damage him.´┐¢
Disband your group and try again.´┐¢ I have been meaning to do this my self
and would be very interested in hearing your results.´┐¢ Please post what your
find and include your stats during the duel (level, str, ac, atk, etc.) and
what songs did what dmg. Both with and without instruments.
´┐¢
Sylly.

-----Original Message-----
From: Robert Maze [mailto:rmaze@...]
Sent: Monday, August 09, 1999 1:57 AM
To: eqbards@onelist.com
Subject: [eqbards] Dueling with AoE songs


Ok I wanted to see what my AoE song's damages were tonite so I dueled a
friend of mine.´┐¢ I had seen other people document what their's did so I was
going to see for myself.´┐¢ Well we did the typical /duel to each other and my

lights when I first started them and then nothing.´┐¢ I did a bellow and he
took damage.´┐¢ What am I missing?´┐¢ He is a level 28 by the way, but I dont
see what the level difference would have to do with it, besides him kicking
my butt.´┐¢ 8)
